          Do you want to put your knowledge into practice as quickly as possible,  be part of competent teams and broaden your personal and professional  horizons? Then come and join HeidelbergCement, contribute to our  success and develop your strengths at the same time. Take the  opportunity to combine your individual career goals with our corporate  goals. In return, you can expect Group-wide induction programmes – for  technical graduates in technology, mechanical engineering, process  engineering, chemical engineering, mining, stones &amp; earth or  mineralogy as well as for graduates in the disciplines of business  administration (finance, controlling, logistics) and IT.
          The induction programmes feature extensive personnel development  measures – both at Group level and in the individual countries. For  example, this includes advanced training offers in the areas of  leadership and management, business administration, sales, cement  production, quality management and IT. Foreign languages, project work  and assignments abroad for managers or experts are also covered by  these programmes.<br />
